Author: payfrit
Title: Announcing the Payfrit RMS ICO. comments and input appreciated.
Body: Website - http://www.payfrit.com  Whitepaper (google docs) - https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Em98l_Zzsg6vHjyZm6rZUXT50ArX85RpF-HyGkgCsYE/edit?usp=sharing  Slide deck for Payfrit RMS (google slides) - https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1MzEHPS3c2e--t2NxJiqLPVIWq2yIl-49a332YvFp6ig/edit?usp=sharing  Please contact us for additional information or questions.  Available @payfrit on all major communication platforms.  One hour turnaround time during normal business hours for Los Angeles, CA, USA.  email payfrit *at* gmail.com   Payfrit RMS is a blended placement offering.  Participation is available to all accredited investors, non-accredited USA residents who provide KYC info, and also via crypto token sale.
